    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Because of an editing error, an article in The Arts yesterday about a high-definition video projection system that can put an actor's image on stage next to him omitted the opening date for the play ''Losing Something,'' which will mark the first use of the system by an American theater company. Previews begin tonight at the 3LD Art &amp; Technology Center in Lower Manhattan, and the official opening is Friday.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
